Package net.runelite.api

Class Varbits

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.runelite.api.Varbits
  • public final class Varbits
extends Object
    Server controlled "content-developer" integers.
    See Also:
    These differ from a in that VarBits can be less than 32 bits. One or more VarBits can be assigned to a backing VarPlayer, each with a static range of bits that it is allowed to access. This allows a more compact representation of small values, like booleans
